--> lambda filter() , map(), reduce()

	-> filter()

		* filter that takes a sequence as an argument and this will filter out all the elements in sqeuence
		*  output have to mention the data type to print

		* syntax:
			x= filter(lambda args: expression , sequence element )


	->map()

		* the map() in lambda that takes a sequence as an argument and a sequence is returned
		* the expression in map that applies to all elements in the sequence
		* syntax:
			* x= map(lambda args: expression , sequence element )


